<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Task Due Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            color: #333333;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #007bff; /* Blue color for title */
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .accent {
            color: #007bff; /* Blue color for accent */
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007bff; /* Blue color for links */
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .logo {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 80px; /* Adjusted the width of the logo */
        }
        .message-container {
            background-color: #f2f2f2; /* Light gray background for message container */
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .task-name {
            color: #007bff; /* Blue color for task name */
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .list-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<div class="container">
  <div class="container" style="background-color: #333333; color: #ffffff; padding: 20px;">
    <div class="message-container" style="text-align: center; color: #333333;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 24px;">Task Due Reminder</h1>
        <img src="https://iili.io/JwWRQou.md.png" alt="PennyWise Logo" style="width: 150px; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="font-size: 14px;">Dear user,</p>
        <p class="task-name" style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: #333333; font-weight: bold;">Task:</span> <span class="accent" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">{{ task.descriptiontask }}</span></p>
        <p class="list-name" style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: #333333; font-weight: bold;">List:</span> <span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">{{ listName }}</span></p>
        <p style="font-size: 14px;">This is a friendly reminder that the above task is due in <span style="font-weight: bold;">TWO Days</span>.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 14px;">Please make sure to complete it on time.</p>
    </div>
     <p class="footer" style="font-size: 14px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;">Best regards,<br> PennyWise Team</p>
</div>


</div>
</body>
</html>
